OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784722710
OL,3,CSouthampton FC's head coach Tonda
OL,4,CEckert charged with misconduct over
OL,5,C'spygate'
OL,7,FSouthampton's head coach Tonda Eckert
OL,8,Fhas been charged by the Football
OL,9,FAssociation over the 'Spygate' scandal.
OL,11,FSaints were thrown out of the
OL,12,FChampionship play-offs by the EFL in
OL,13,FMay over the affair and docked four
OL,14,Fpoints for the coming season.
OL,16,FThe club admitted spying on a training
OL,17,Fsession held by play-off opponents
OL,18,FMiddlesbrough in May, and on sessions
OL,19,Fat Ipswich and Oxford earlier in the
OL,20,Fseason.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
