FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784722710
OL,3,CSouthampton FC's head coach Tonda
OL,4,CEckert charged with misconduct over
OL,5,C'spygate'
OL,7,FOn May 21 the FA confirmed it was
OL,8,Finvestigating the matter, and on
OL,9,FWednesday it announced charges had
OL,10,Fbeen brought.
OL,12,FIn a statement the FA said:
OL,13,F"Southampton FC's Tonda Eckert has
OL,14,Fbeen charged with three breaches of FA
OL,15,FRule E3.1 in relation to misconduct
OL,16,Fbetween December 2025 and May 2026.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784722710
OL,3,CSouthampton FC's head coach Tonda
OL,4,CEckert charged with misconduct over
OL,5,C'spygate'
OL,7,F"It's alleged that the head coach
OL,8,Facted in an improper manner and/or
OL,9,Fbrought the game into disrepute by
OL,10,Fdirecting and/or authorising the
OL,11,Fobservation of training sessions of
OL,12,FOxford United FC, Ipswich Town FC and
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough FC ahead of fixtures
OL,14,Fbetween these clubs and Southampton FC
OL,15,Fin December 2025, April 2026 and May
OL,16,F2026 respectively.
OL,18,F"Tonda Eckert has until Tuesday 28
OL,19,FJuly 2026 to provide his responses."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
