PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784722710
OL,3,CSouthampton FC's head coach Tonda
OL,4,CEckert charged with misconduct over
OL,5,C'spygate'
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Southampton FC
OL,8,Fsaid: "Tonda and the club will
OL,9,Fcontinue to cooperate fully and openly
OL,10,Fwith The FA.
OL,12,F"Our focus remains on preparations for
OL,13,Fthe 2026/27 Championship season. The
OL,14,Fclub remains fully supportive of Tonda
OL,15,Fand his staff as we work towards our
OL,16,Fambition of returning to the Premier
OL,17,FLeague.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
