PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784722710
OL,3,CSouthampton FC's head coach Tonda
OL,4,CEckert charged with misconduct over
OL,5,C'spygate'
OL,7,F"We are unable to comment further
OL,8,Fwhile the process remains ongoing, but
OL,9,Fwe will provide an update to
OL,10,Fsupporters as soon as we are in a
OL,11,Fposition to do so."
OL,13,FThis is a breaking story, more to
OL,14,Ffollow.
